Package: WTPBr
Type: Package
Title: Brazil road travel Survey - VTTS and VSL estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tatiana Ferrari, Luiza Dusi, Fabiano Pompemayer
Maintainer: Tatiana Ferrari <tatianak.ferrari@gmail.com>
Description: This package was created to share data and demostrate the application of the Mixed Logit Model, a Discrete Choice model analysis, 
    for the estimation of the value of Statistical Life (VSL) and the Value of Travel Time Saving (VTTS). The data is based on a Survey with road passengers in Brazil, conducted by the Institute of Applied Economic Research in 2017. 
     For detailed information and results discussion see: 
     FERRARI, T.; DUSI, L.; LOPES, D.;POMPEMAYER, F. Estimativa do valor da vida estatística e valor da economia de tempo em viagens nas rodovias brasileiras
     com a utilização de pesquisa de preferência declarada. Brasilia: IPEA, 2019. (Texto para Discussão). 
